{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1bb795d96e","title":"复刘伯承、邓小平等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"64fe73474d","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":20,"articleId":"1bb795d96e"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"606de02fc9","type":"paragraph","text":"复刘伯承、邓小平等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1bb795d96e"},{"id":"63dc8ed35e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年7月20日）司意刘、邓率野战司令部进至菏泽地区，三纵进至朝城、县地区待机。[1]20日，刘伯承、邓小平致电中类军委，建议先将野战军领导机关移至湾泽。这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的复刘伯承、邓小平并告陈毅、宋时轮电的主要内容。26日，毛泽东又为中共中央军委起草复电，指出：“对院海线总以准备充分、攻击奏效为原则，时间上可的量推退数天，一初由你们依前线情况决定。”原定南线7月底外线出击的计划就此后推。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1bb795d96e"}],"page":{"id":"2258d58ad7","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"1bb795d96e","start":512,"end":512}}}},"__N_SSG":true}